05:33.500 --> 05:35.742
Come on, buddy,
you're embarrassing me.

05:35.894 --> 05:36.893
<i> They did it.</i>

05:36.912 --> 05:38.003
<i> They signed the contract</i>

05:38.230 --> 05:40.505
<i> that would make</i>
<i> their cocaine dealer rich.</i>

05:40.657 --> 05:41.915
<i> And then it was off</i>
<i> to the studio</i>

05:42.009 --> 05:43.592
